node.text: There are so many amazing things about @getyourteachon, but one of my absolute favorites is the people💗It’s always so crazy to think that this little app brought us all together from all across the country!! The GYTO fam has the most genuine, uplifting, positive, caring people in the world. I love these humans so much & I can’t wait to see everyone in Atlanta in October!!! Find your people. It’s important with this crazy career we have all chosen. (Also Instagram can we get an update bc I need to be able to post more than 10 pics, thnx🤣) #gyto #getyourteachon #gytoxorlando

node.text:
It’s time to start shopping for back to school!! #ad Every year growing up my mom would take me to buy a new pair of sneakers for the new school year. I LOVED this back to school tradition (along with buying all the school supplies of course🙈). I headed to @DSW to grab a few pairs of shoes to kick start the new school year😉 From tennis shoes to keep up my workout routine from the summer, to classic white sneakers that can be worn throughout the entire school week, DSW has got you covered! #mydsw

✨New Balance Fresh Foam X70
✨Reebok Club Memt 
✨Cloud Running Shoe

You can shop all these looks via the @shop.ltk app! Just search maniacsinthemiddle!

node.text: I promise this is not a home decor Instagram🤣 & I will get back to regularly scheduled teacher content come August, but I gotta say it’s been REAL nice not thinking about school this summer🙌🏼 I was the teacher that was constantly working on projects all summer long & knocking at our custodians door to get in my classroom. After the EXHAUSTING year we had, I just needed a LONG mental break from teaching & it has been so refreshing!! Teaching content coming soon, don’t worry😉 PS everything is linked in my stories or home highlight🏡

node.text: Hey, MTV! Welcome to my crib🏡 I BOUGHT A HOUSE🥳 This has been a huge goal of mine for the past 2 years & I honestly still can’t believe it came true on Wednesday!!😭 The house hunting process was crazy & I could not have done it without @amandawithremax 💓Thanks to everyone for the sweet messages over the past couple of days. I truly feel overwhelmed with all the support from my friends, family, & all of you! I promise I will get back to teaching content soon, but I will for sure be sharing a few home things along the way!! #homeowner

node.text: 28 trips around the sun☀️🌎🚀✨(+ 1 day) I have a love/hate relationship with my birthday because it means summer is halfway over💔Anyone else feel that way about the 4th of July?? node.text:
It’s not quite time to start PLANNING for next school year, but it is time to start customizing your PLANNER!! Think of any popular teacher planner & I have tried it. This planner from @4theloveofpi is my ride or die planner & I won’t ever go back to anything else! What I love most is that it is 100% customizable from the cover, the the number of subjects, & even what subjects you teach! Here’s what I ordered this year:

⭐️The non-teacher planner (I know you’re probably thinking I’m nuts🤣 But as a middle school teacher I have 150 students. I don’t use the class rosters, parent emails, etc that come in the teacher planner. I actually chatted with Amie about what my best option was & she recommended the non-teacher planner for middle school teachers!)
⭐️One subject. (This year I am only teaching 5 sections of science🙌🏼. Last year I ordered the 2 subject planner since I taught Science & one section of writing!)
⭐️Boho #7 cover with my name on it
⭐️I also ordered a notebook to match! 
⭐️Bonus points for this planner because sticky notes fit perfectly inside👏🏼

This is not an ad either!! Megan (@mathtothe6thpower) actually was the first to order this planner & now our whole team uses them🤣🙌🏼 I just genuinely love this planner & want to share it with the world!

Get Your Teach On is less than a month away & I couldn’t be more excited!!😍 GYTO always makes me come home ready to implement new strategies into my classroom! This year more than ever I am excited to get re-energized from that GYTO spirit for the upcoming school year🥳 I will be presenting 3 sessions so let me know which room I will be seeing you in down below👇🏼 

⭐️GYTO’s Wide World of STEAM with @chrispombonyo for grades 2-4!
⭐️Seatbelts Everyone! with @cook_in_the_classroom for grades 5-12!
⭐️Tech Time with @cook_in_the_classroom for grades 7-12! 

If you’re headed to Get Your Teach On in Orlando make sure you pre-order your merch to pick up at the conference!! Head to shop.getyourteachon.com!
